    • setup

      public void setup​(GameManager gameManager)
      Description copied from interface: ManagerInterface
      Initialises this UI and sets up the given RocketManager with the rockets to be managed. Note that setup need not be complete by the time this method returns. Once setup is complete this UI must call gameManager.
      Specified by:
      setup in interface ManagerInterface
      Parameters:
